				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/B%C3%ACnh-Ng%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-c%C3%A1o/poem-mLEGY5d9nFI0RH280X-vIQ">Bình Ngô đại cáo - 平吳大告</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C3%A1i-T%E1%BB%95/Chinh-ho%C3%A0n-qu%C3%A1-Bi%E1%BB%87n-kh%E1%BA%A9u-ng%E1%BB%99-b%E1%BA%A1o-phong-s%E1%BA%ADu-v%C5%A9-%C4%91%E1%BA%A3o-vu-thi%C3%AAn/poem-102RW_3SlibLWJMV72QGXA">Chinh hoàn quá Biện khẩu, ngộ bạo phong sậu vũ, đảo vu thiên - 征還過汴口，遇暴風驟雨，禱于天</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C3%A1i-T%E1%BB%95/author-1RfRsGNVNQbtjX629ZNHvQ">Lý Thái Tổ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Canh/poem-nBl-nnIR3etTnaJQ2c_w6g">Hương Canh - 香羹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/author-0k6qEpgf02Latsw5cZPrXg">Khiếu Năng Tĩnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/Long-M%C3%B4n-than/poem-aq7Xlki-ZiKUgiWo_BOxNg">Long Môn than - 龍門灘</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/author--99oPAxPzhbe5OwOvLz_qg">Lê Giản</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Di-T%C3%B4n/Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-%C4%91%E1%BB%9Bi-sinh-ca/poem-XGDV-KqgVFWcId2MqnewVg">Ngọc đới sinh ca - 玉帶生歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Di-T%C3%B4n/author-edTceA8S1YU0BsK54Tjq9Q">Chu Di Tôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Nh%E1%BA%ADp-H%C3%A0nh-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-RaTSZaUHzh49rWc6QXWeqw">Nhập Hành Châu - 入衡州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%E1%BB%9F-v%C5%A9-b%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-quy-Nh%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C3%A2y-cam-l%C3%A2m/poem-M53RSlFcPrFgDdYAitDzcg">Trở vũ bất đắc quy Nhương Tây cam lâm - 阻雨不得歸瀼西甘林</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/T%E1%BB%AB-%C3%82n-t%E1%BB%B1-bi-minh-t%E1%BB%8Bnh-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-CmcW-aGSq0U6WnbHUzXRPg">Từ Ân tự bi minh tịnh tự - 慈恩寺碑銘并序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/author-AQI-nV6p-JhBHd--0I9cWA">Hồ Tông Thốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/Vi%E1%BB%87t-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-th%C3%A1o/poem-9mQmZ8x8fISxAb3ca2fflg">Việt Thường tháo - 越裳操</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%A1-L%C3%A3m/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-B%C3%A1o-Thi%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%B1-th%C3%A1p/poem-AbW3pF51_pg3sDTG-9BrlQ">Vịnh Báo Thiên tự tháp - 詠報天寺塔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%A1-L%C3%A3m/author-9ppkdEWSUlq0gOg71v0QIQ">Trần Bá Lãm</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
